{"tid":1716141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教育局宣布明日全港學校停課","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:22:56.000Z","uid":254898,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5371068cf4210420cd882588d3a9969f4b8dd24b","tid":1716141,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:20:06.000Z","msg":"【14:10】教育局宣布，因應當前及可預計的交通狀況，及全港學校整體匯報，全港學校(包括幼稚園、小學、中學及特殊學校)將於明日(14日)停課。當局呼籲學童留在家中，不要在街上流連，遠離危險，更切勿參加違法活動，而各學校須保持校舍開放，並安排教職員在安全情況下回校照顧學生。<br />\n<br />\n今日香港，警察獨大，政權腐敗<br />\n我地默然接受，佢地就得寸進尺<br />\n我地既民權一直被剝削<br />\n繼續行使我地既義務實屬荒唐<br />\n勞動力既成果都歸於一批剝削我地既人實屬反智<br />\n因此我地發起三罷，路本來就係我地既<br />\n權利係我地生而有之<br />\n冇權利更不能假設義務係理所當然<br />\n我地冇唔比人返工返學<br />\n我地只係要比所有人都能夠發揮自由意志<br />\n有權利能夠選擇罷工，罷課，罷市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74aaca3286de4ebf0097bfcabe82d2ac4b8fa3ae","tid":1716141,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"停課搞得成啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf6b8192fc631f86798d54239dcc76d12ed2907","tid":1716141,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"Twitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=a02a1f02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> /task</strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"dc996f82333babcf3bb283a9a8b2215506221dfb","tid":1716141,"uid":257567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"瞓咗幾耐"},{"pid":"e9403ef42cfcff93d8f46a79737d5d0a68010ccf","tid":1716141,"uid":254898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc996f82333babcf3bb283a9a8b2215506221dfb","tid":1716141,"uid":257567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"瞓咗幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"扮瞓咗三日，終於覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}